               stealing, on the <rs id="t18301209-268-cd1501" type="crimeDate">30th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-268-off1500 t18301209-268-cd1501"></join>, 1 shirt, value 4s., and 1 waistcoat, value 3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18301209-268-victim2247" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Atkins
                  <interp inst="t18301209-268-victim2247" type="surname" value="Atkins"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18301209-268-victim2247" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
